WEBVTT

00:12.888 --> 00:15.349
- [sniffing]
- [siren wailing]

00:15.433 --> 00:17.727
[growls, barking]

00:17.810 --> 00:18.811
[gunfire]

00:23.858 --> 00:25.818
♪ ♪

00:25.901 --> 00:27.903
[monitor beeping steadily]

00:34.410 --> 00:36.328
[doctor] I'm afraid
it won't be long now.

00:36.412 --> 00:38.581
A couple of days at most.

00:38.664 --> 00:40.666
I'm sorry...

01:03.355 --> 01:05.316
[sighs]

01:10.321 --> 01:12.323
[sniffling]

01:13.491 --> 01:15.493
[sobbing]

01:29.799 --> 01:31.592
[gasps softly]

01:31.675 --> 01:33.844
[inhales]

01:41.519 --> 01:43.479
[footfalls on pavement]

02:03.290 --> 02:04.708
[squeaking softly]

02:16.804 --> 02:19.473
Hey! Looking sharp, old-timer.

02:19.557 --> 02:21.225
Thank you, Gary, um...

02:21.308 --> 02:23.936
could you a... uh...
could you do me a favor?

02:24.019 --> 02:25.563
Sure, buddy. What do you need?

02:25.646 --> 02:28.232
The-the tap is stuck
in the closet over here

02:28.315 --> 02:30.776
and my arthritis is,
uh, painful.

02:30.860 --> 02:33.195
So could you, uh, help?

02:33.279 --> 02:35.948
[sighs]
Sure, why not?

02:39.034 --> 02:40.703
What, are you losing it, John?

02:40.786 --> 02:42.913
- These are fine.
- [grunts]

02:42.997 --> 02:45.291
Uh, what are you doing there,
Johnny?

02:45.374 --> 02:47.710
[panting]

02:47.793 --> 02:49.378
Okay, very funny, man.

02:49.461 --> 02:51.714
- [zapping]
- [shouting]

02:54.341 --> 02:56.760
[panting]

03:02.933 --> 03:04.518
[scanner beeps]

03:05.978 --> 03:07.062
[grunts]

03:13.652 --> 03:15.988
[moaning]

03:18.157 --> 03:19.783
Sun-Hee?

03:19.867 --> 03:22.661
John... John?

03:25.372 --> 03:27.917
What...? What did you do?

03:28.000 --> 03:29.543
I got you medicine.

03:33.297 --> 03:35.925
What do you mean?
[shouting]

03:36.008 --> 03:38.010
Sun-Hee?! Nurse!

03:38.093 --> 03:40.137
- Nurse!
- Hands up, come on!

03:45.517 --> 03:48.187
It was me. Don't hurt her!

03:48.270 --> 03:50.522
What's happening?

03:50.606 --> 03:51.732
[both gasp]

03:51.815 --> 03:53.817
- Sir?
- Fuck.

03:53.901 --> 03:56.111
Okay, cover her,
get him in cuffs.

03:56.195 --> 03:58.614
Please, she didn't do anything.
She's sick!

03:58.697 --> 04:00.532
[grunting]

04:00.616 --> 04:02.034
Pancreatic cancer.

04:02.117 --> 04:03.911
Make it look natural.

04:03.994 --> 04:05.704
No! No!

04:05.788 --> 04:06.830
Honey!

04:06.914 --> 04:09.708
- John!
- Please, stop!

04:09.792 --> 04:11.168
John!

04:11.251 --> 04:12.336
Honey!

04:12.419 --> 04:15.005
[grunting]

04:17.174 --> 04:19.218
[screaming]

04:19.301 --> 04:21.512
[grunting]

04:21.595 --> 04:23.430
- [gunshots]
- [shouting]

04:31.313 --> 04:33.315
[panting]

04:37.611 --> 04:39.697
John, what happened?

04:39.780 --> 04:41.657
Did I do that?

04:43.117 --> 04:44.410
We have to go.

04:44.493 --> 04:45.786
Honey!

04:50.165 --> 04:51.834
- [gasps]
- Huh?

04:51.917 --> 04:53.460
Fire!

04:53.544 --> 04:54.670
No! Please!

04:54.753 --> 04:56.672
[gunfire]

05:01.844 --> 05:03.137
Huh?

05:03.220 --> 05:05.431
[guard] Whoa! What the fuck?

05:05.514 --> 05:08.017
[grunting]

05:18.610 --> 05:21.405
[all grunting]

05:27.244 --> 05:29.747
[screaming]

05:33.167 --> 05:35.544
[exhales]
Oh, my God.

05:35.627 --> 05:38.088
- [panting]
- It's okay.

05:38.172 --> 05:40.382
They were trying
to kill us first.

05:40.466 --> 05:41.884
[Sun-Hee] I don't think
it's okay.

05:41.967 --> 05:42.885
- We have to go.
- John,

05:42.968 --> 05:45.345
I don't think it's okay.

05:48.599 --> 05:51.935
[John] There's a cabin.
Three hours away.

05:52.019 --> 05:53.729
I rented it.
We can go there first

05:53.812 --> 05:55.856
- and, uh...
- What did you do to me?

05:57.524 --> 05:59.902
It doesn't matter.
What matters is you're better.

05:59.985 --> 06:03.238
- I'm not better.
- You're alive. Look at you.

06:03.322 --> 06:05.032
You haven't been able to walk
in months.

06:05.115 --> 06:06.617
See? Look.

06:06.700 --> 06:09.495
And we have time now.
Time for everything.

06:12.372 --> 06:15.667
This isn't how things
are supposed to be.

06:15.751 --> 06:17.336
Well, you weren't supposed
to get sick, either.

06:17.419 --> 06:19.671
John...
[groaning loudly]

06:19.755 --> 06:21.423
What's wrong? What's happening?

06:24.051 --> 06:25.511
Pull over. Please.

06:25.594 --> 06:27.262
- [panting]
- No, we can't.
We need to keep...

06:27.346 --> 06:28.597
[yells]

06:28.680 --> 06:29.890
[tires screech]

06:30.933 --> 06:32.851
[Sun-Hee panting]

06:32.935 --> 06:34.561
Sun-Hee!

06:35.562 --> 06:36.939
- Sun-Hee! Sun-Hee!
- [grunting]

06:37.022 --> 06:38.565
Sun-Hee!

06:40.609 --> 06:42.402
[John grunting]

06:44.863 --> 06:46.865
[grunts]

06:46.949 --> 06:49.368
[Sun-Hee groaning, grunting]

06:49.451 --> 06:51.829
[John gasping]

06:51.912 --> 06:54.081
[whimpers, screams]

06:54.164 --> 06:57.251
[pulsing, squelching]

07:13.183 --> 07:15.686
[John grunts]

07:15.769 --> 07:18.021
[animals chittering]

07:29.283 --> 07:32.870
[screaming]

07:39.251 --> 07:40.836
[bear growling]

07:50.679 --> 07:54.474
[roars]

07:54.558 --> 07:57.186
[both grunt]

07:58.228 --> 07:59.563
[both gasp]

07:59.646 --> 08:02.149
[deep rumbling]

08:02.232 --> 08:03.859
[gunfire]

08:11.325 --> 08:12.701
[roaring]

08:12.784 --> 08:15.245
[gasping]

08:16.330 --> 08:20.334
[grunting, screaming]

08:20.417 --> 08:22.544
[John grunts]

08:29.593 --> 08:31.553
[engine sputtering]

08:34.306 --> 08:36.934
See, this is good.
The cancer's gone.

08:37.017 --> 08:39.353
John, it's not gone.

08:39.436 --> 08:40.854
That's not our problem.

08:40.938 --> 08:44.316
It came from me
because of what you did.

08:44.399 --> 08:47.069
[engine starts]

08:47.152 --> 08:50.364
Once we're safe, we can call
the police. The army.

08:50.447 --> 08:53.533
John, we have to stay and help.

08:53.617 --> 08:56.620
There's nothing we can do.
It'll kill us.

08:58.080 --> 09:00.582
We have to try.

09:00.666 --> 09:01.667
Please.

09:09.091 --> 09:11.093
[crying]

09:17.182 --> 09:21.687
No. Not now.
I just got you back.

09:21.770 --> 09:24.273
[crying]

09:25.941 --> 09:29.653
[low growling]

09:35.117 --> 09:36.660
[gasps]

09:36.743 --> 09:38.745
[pulsing, squelching]

09:45.627 --> 09:48.839
It's so big. We can't.

09:48.922 --> 09:51.842
[inhales, grunts]

09:51.925 --> 09:53.343
You should stay back.

09:53.427 --> 09:55.721
I think I...
[screams]

09:58.181 --> 09:59.349
[John grunts]

10:01.268 --> 10:02.853
Sun-Hee!

10:08.191 --> 10:09.985
Leave her alone!

10:12.863 --> 10:14.364
[John grunts]

10:16.742 --> 10:19.036
[roaring]

10:19.119 --> 10:20.704
[gasps]

10:27.461 --> 10:29.296
[gasps softly]

10:42.392 --> 10:44.394
[roaring]

10:45.687 --> 10:47.647
I'm sorry.

10:52.319 --> 10:54.613
It's okay.

10:59.117 --> 11:01.453
Don't worry about me. Now, go.

11:04.748 --> 11:06.583
Hurry and go.

11:18.512 --> 11:21.890
Don't forget to eat on time.

11:25.435 --> 11:28.814
Don't skip meals
just because I'm not there.

11:29.648 --> 11:31.858
[shouts]

11:35.404 --> 11:37.406
♪ ♪

12:07.102 --> 12:09.855
♪ ♪

12:35.130 --> 12:36.840
♪ ♪
